  "texts": [
    "The network has five graph convolutional blocks.",
    "In the first two graph convolution blocks, all ligand and receptor atoms 5 Å apart from each other are considered, and 64 filters per block are used.",
    "In the third block, the cutoff radius and filters are increased to 7 Å and 128, respectively.",
    "Only ligand features in the last two blocks are considered without changing the threshold cutoff or the number of filters.",
    "Finally, the sum-pool of the ligandonly layer creates a 3-task layer on top of the network."
  ],
